==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Transpare
<hw>Trans*pare"</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>v. t. & i.</pos> <ety>[See
<er>Transparent</er>.]</ety> <def>To be, or cause to be, transparent; to
appear, or cause to appear, or be seen, through something.</def>
<mark>[Obs.]</mark> <rj><au>Stirling.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Transparence</ent>⟦br⟧
